---
// Footer.astro - Premium Lightweight Beige Footer
---

<footer class="bg-brand-sand border-t border-brand-sand/60 pt-12 pb-6 select-none mt-16">
  <div class="container-main">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 pb-8">
      <!-- Columna 1: Logo & Propósito (5 cols en desktop) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-5 flex flex-col items-start gap-4 animate-fadeInUp">
        <span class="font-serif text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark tracking-wide">
          Magna Propiedades
        </span>
        <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-brand-dark/70 leading-relaxed max-w-sm">
          Curaduría de propiedades exclusivas y servicios inmobiliarios integrales. Acompañamos tu inversión con asesoramiento profesional de alta gama en cada etapa.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Columna 2: Navegación (3 cols en desktop) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-3 flex flex-col gap-3 animate-fadeInUp delay-100">
        <h3 class="text-[10px] font-bold text-brand-sage uppercase tracking-wider">
          Navegación
        </h3>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <li><a href="/" class="text-xs text-brand-dark/85 hover:text-brand-sage transition-colors font-medium">Inicio</a></li>
          <li><a href="/catalogo" class="text-xs text-brand-dark/85 hover:text-brand-sage transition-colors font-medium">Catálogo</a></li>
          <li><a href="/#servicios" class="text-xs text-brand-dark/85 hover:text-brand-sage transition-colors font-medium">Servicios</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Columna 3: Legal (4 cols en desktop) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-4 flex flex-col gap-3 animate-fadeInUp delay-200">
        <h3 class="text-[10px] font-bold text-brand-sage uppercase tracking-wider">
          Legal
        </h3>
        <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <li><a href="/privacidad" class="text-xs text-brand-dark/85 hover:text-brand-sage transition-colors font-medium">Privacidad</a></li>
          <li><a href="/terminos" class="text-xs text-brand-dark/85 hover:text-brand-sage transition-colors font-medium">Términos y Condiciones</a></li>
          <li><span class="text-xs text-brand-dark/85 font-medium">Oficina: San Martín 308, Trelew</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Barra Inferior de Copyright y Redes -->
    <div class="border-t border-brand-dark/10 pt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-brand-dark/65 font-medium">
        &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Magna Propiedades. Todos los derechos reservados.
      </p>

      <!-- Redes e Iconos Sociales -->
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 animate-fadeIn">
        <a 
          href="https://instagram.com/magnapropiedades.tw" 
          target="_blank" 
          rel="noopener noreferrer" 
          class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-brand-dark/10 hover:border-brand-sage hover:bg-white text-brand-dark hover:text-brand-sage flex items-center justify-center transition-all"
          aria-label="Instagram Magna Propiedades"
        >
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect width="20" height="20" x="2" y="2" rx="5" ry="5"/>
            <path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"/>
            <line x1="17.5" x2="17.51" y1="6.5" y2="6.5"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        
        <a 
          href="https://facebook.com/magna.propiedad" 
          target="_blank" 
          rel="noopener noreferrer" 
          class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border border-brand-dark/10 hover:border-brand-sage hover:bg-white text-brand-dark hover:text-brand-sage flex items-center justify-center transition-all"
          aria-label="Facebook Magna Propiedades"
        >
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
